Class Converter

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.machadolucas.dataconverter.Converter

  • public class Converter
extends java.lang.Object

    Main class of the dataconverter library.

    You can use its methods to convert data between CSV, TSV and JSON formats.

        Converts a CSV String to a JSON String
        Parameters:
        csv - a String with data separated with commas (,) and lines (\n). For example: "COLUMN1,COLUMN2\ndataX1,dataX2\ndataY1,dataY2"
        Returns:
        the data in a array of JSON objects String. For example: "[{\"COLUMN1\":dataX1,\" COLUMN2\":dataX2},{\"COLUMN1\":dataY1,\"COLUMN2\":dataY2}]"
